Try
```python
    def user_illusts(self, user_id, illust_type=None, illust_filter='for_ios', offset=None, req_auth=False):
        url = 'https://app-api.pixiv.net/v1/user/illusts'
        params = {
            'user_id': user_id,
            'filter': illust_filter
        }
        if illust_type:
